that's a known bug for Dolphin, however there's a workaround to bypass it.
before starting the game, go to Sound Plugin settings, Uncheck all the three options, and put volume to 1, and switch Dsound to Openal. now play the game, defeat the Boss, after the game saves, you can return everything to normal. anyway, you have to do this for every Boss

